  "detailed_description": "Future Pool is a futuristic and dynamic variation of 8-ball pool. Players take turns to fire a glassy cue-ball at a cluster of balls on a circular pool table. The first player to knock out all of their balls plus the black 8-ball is the winner. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay against a choice of computer opponents on a choice of table designs, or play against a friend on your PC. You can also compete in a 6-player tournament, and any player can be human or computer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControl the game using mouse or keyboard or an X-Box style game controller.",
  "about_the_game": "Future Pool is a futuristic and dynamic variation of 8-ball pool. Players take turns to fire a glassy cue-ball at a cluster of balls on a circular pool table. The first player to knock out all of their balls plus the black 8-ball is the winner. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay against a choice of computer opponents on a choice of table designs, or play against a friend on your PC. You can also compete in a 6-player tournament, and any player can be human or computer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControl the game using mouse or keyboard or an X-Box style game controller.",
